accessibility.text: Tasks To Complete Ahead Of Training
Practice Manager completes practice questionnaire that provides PatientFi data on:
Current product offering in regards to financing, how it’s presented, as well as when and where patients apply
Top 5 procedures offered and pricing to determine “down payment” requirements
Identifying any customization needed within the PatientFi platform (i.e. no 48 month term, special 0% offers, etc.)
Currently working on monthly surgical offer single page handouts to be included with these
Create custom HTML web banner/application link for practice website and send to practice
Introduce the Learning Center to practice manager and staff - Ready January 1
Send certification quiz to staff so they can start to formulate ideas and questions prior to training
Send digital version of training guide to staff
